<paragraph blockId="27.[189,1399,377,544]" pageId="27" pageNumber="133">Eyes almost bare; face and frontal triangle shiny black, without polinosity; antennae reddish-orange, basoflagellomere oval; scutum and scutellum shiny black, without median pollinose vittae; metafemur distinctly enlarged, mostly orange with exception of black apex; metatibia black; wing hyaline; abdomen predominantly orange.</paragraph>
